name: ASCII Grampa
description: Winston Golding; my grandfather and an amazing soul overall transitioned on August 25, 2021 at University Hospital in Jamaica. He leaves behind a wonderful legacy not just in the form of children, grandchildren and great grandchildren; but also via his wife and other relatives. As well as the legacy carved out involving reggae music and his amazing writings. So many lives touched, so many stories and so little time. Thank you for all you have done.
